author: Evelyn Cheng
title: For some Chinese businesses, there's no going back to life before the coronavirus
description: As the second quarter begins in China, it's an altered landscape in the coronavirus-stricken economy with businesses that remain shut — some for good.
content:
This photo taken on March 23, 2020 shows employees eating during lunch break at an auto plant of Dongfeng Honda in Wuhan in China's central Hubei province.
